        "question_AYijQm": {
          "type": "question",
          "name": "Can I change or cancel my order?",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I change or cancel my order?",
            "answer": "<p>Please contact our team ASAP if you need to make any changes to your order! Either via live chat, phone or email at <a href=\"mailto:orders@beserk.com.au\">orders@beserk.com.au</a>. ❤</p><p>We aim to pack & dispatch all orders as soon as possible - so whilst we will do our best to change your order, unfortunately if you don't contact us quickly it may be too late. Please reach out to us and we will see what we can do!</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_yeATM3": {
          "type": "question",
          "name": "Will my order be packaged securely?",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Will my order be packaged securely?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes! We take extra time and care to make sure all parcels are sent with appropriate packaging to keep them safe.</p><p>Although we take extra care to avoid damage, sometimes the Australia Post delivery drivers do not know their own strength. If you do receive your order and it has been broken during transit please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:orders@beserk.com.au\">orders@beserk.com.au</a> with a photo of the item so we can assist you ASAP!</p>"
          }
        },
