        "question_9q4YB7": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you accept Returns?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes we do! Shop with confidence as we have a <strong>BESERK 30 DAY RETURN GUARANTEE </strong>❤️</p><ul><li>You can return your order within 30 DAYS for a<strong> REFUND, STORE CREDIT</strong> or <strong>EXCHANGE</strong>*<br/>*Sale items can be exchanged for STORE CREDIT Only.</li><li>ALL items can be returned EXCEPT Final Sale products & those under Australian Health & Hygiene regulations [underwear, bodysuits, wigs, swimwear, contact lenses, face masks, hosiery, earrings, cosmetics, hair dye]</li><li>Gift Cards, Throne & YouPay Orders cannot be returned.  </li></ul><p></p><p><strong>To see more information head to our Returns page </strong><a href=\"/pages/beserk-returns\" title=\"Returns\"><strong>HERE</strong></a><strong>!</strong></p>"
          }
        },
        "question_QFQwx6": {
          "type": "question",
          "name": "How do I return make a return?",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do I return make a return?",
            "answer": "<p><strong>Within Australia?<br/></strong>We offer a flat rate return postage of $11.95. Simply <a href=\"https://return.auspost.com.au/BESERK\" target=\"_blank\">click here</a>, complete the form and make payment for your postage to generate a return label.<br/><br/>We also offer returns via Refundid for an instant refund! Get your Refundid return started and read <a href=\"/pages/beserk-returns\" title=\"Returns\">more information HERE</a>!</p><p><strong>Local to our Virginia Warehouse?<br/></strong>Drop by the Beserk Warehouse (Monday to Friday - 8.30am to 4.30pm) to process your return with our customer service team at:</p><p><br/>2/58 Yarraman Place,<br/>Virginia, QLD, 4014<strong><br/></strong></p><p><strong>International?<br/></strong>Simply send it back to:<br/><strong>BESERK RETURNS<br/>2/58 Yarraman Place,<br/>Virginia QLD 4014 AUSTRALIA</strong></p><p>Please remember to pop a note in with your return letting us know your order number so we can process it right away.<strong><br/></strong></p><p><strong>To see more information head to our Returns page </strong><a href=\"/pages/beserk-returns\" title=\"Returns\"><strong>HERE</strong></a><strong>!</strong></p>"
          }
        },
        "question_yjkVd9": {
          "type": "question",
          "name": "Do you offer exchanges?",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you offer exchanges?",
            "answer": "<p>We don't offer exchanges via post, sorry! But you can return any eligible items back to us for a full refund or store credit 🖤</p><p><br/><strong>Local to our Beserk Warehouse in Virginia?<br/></strong>You can drop off any eligible items for an exchange or return. Start a live chat or email our team at orders@beserk.com.au with your exchange request so they can help!<strong><br/><br/></strong></p><p><strong>To see more information head to our Returns page </strong><a href=\"/pages/beserk-returns\" title=\"Returns\"><strong>HERE</strong></a><strong>!</strong></p>"
          }
        },
        "question_nb9i8c": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "I have received a Faulty item?",
            "answer": "<p>If you are have received a faulty item, we are very sorry! </p><p>Please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:orders@beserk.com.au\">orders@beserk.com.au</a> with more information on the fault so we can work out a solution for you.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_Epx7iE": {
          "type": "question",
          "name": "How long do I have to return my order?",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How long do I have to return my order?",
            "answer": "<p>You have 30 days (from the date of delivery) to return any eligible items back to us!</p><p><strong>Want to get your return started?</strong> <a href=\"/pages/beserk-returns\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Returns\"><strong>Head to our Returns Page HERE!</strong></a></p>"
          }
        },
        "question_ihHcae": {
          "type": "question",
          "name": "Can I drop off a return at the Warehouse?",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I drop off a return at the Warehouse?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes of course! You can visit our Warehouse to return or exchange any eligible items. We're open 8:30am to 4:30pm Monday to Friday and our address is:<br/><strong><br/>2/58 Yarraman Place,<br/>Virginia QLD 4014 AUSTRALIA</strong></p>"
