        "question_cwJUAT": {
          "type": "question",
          "name": "How long until my return is processed?",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How long until my return is processed?",
            "answer": "<p>We are just a small team but we endeavour to get returns processed ASAP - usually within 5 business days of them arriving at our warehouse. You'll receive an email as soon as we do!</p><p><strong>Been more than 5 business days?<br/></strong>Send us a chat or an email to <a href=\"mailto:orders@beserk.com.au\">orders@beserk.com.au</a> so we can help!</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_MPcV9y": {
          "type": "question",
          "name": "Are any products not eligible for return?",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Are any products not eligible for return?",
            "answer": "<p>Due to Australian Health and Hygiene Regulations, we're unable to accept returns on the following product types:</p><ul><li><strong>Cosmetics </strong>- makeup, skincare, nail polish, perfumes, bath bombs, hair dye, wigs, fangs, contact lenses<br/><br/></li><li><strong>Hosiery </strong>- stockings/tights, socks<br/><br/></li><li><strong>Clothing </strong>- swimwear, bodysuits, underwear<br/><br/></li><li><strong>Jewellery </strong>- earrings, body jewellery<br/><br/></li><li><strong>Final Sale products</strong></li></ul><p>Please ensure products are returned in the same condition they were received in including all tags and packaging where possible. </p><p><strong>Have further questions? </strong>Send a live chat to the team, we're always happy to help!</p>"
          }
        },
