            "answer": "<p>We don't have a store, Beserk is an online shop only.</p><p>But if you live local, you can always place an order for <strong>Click & Collect</strong> and it will usually be ready within 1 hour.</p><p>Need an item sooner? Let us know and we'll do our best to get it ready for you ASAP!</p><p>The Beserk HQ & Warehouse for Pick Ups is located at:<br/><strong><br/>2/58 Yarraman Place,<br/>Virginia QLD 4014 AUSTRALIA</strong></p><p><strong>Please note:</strong> We don't have any change room facilities - sorry!</p>"
