            "answer": "<p>Beserk is a trusted and much loved webstore with 26 years of experience in the online and alternative communities. We take our customers privacy & security very seriously!</p><p>Our customer service team knows that often for a first time buyer, it can be difficult to know who you can trust with your details so you can rest assured that the Beserk webstore is 100% safe & secure.</p><p>You can read our full <a href=\"https://www.beserk.com.au/pages/privacy-policy\" target=\"_blank\">Privacy & Security Policy HERE</a>!</p>"
