        "question_XRFkPM": {
          "type": "question",
          "name": "How do pre-orders work?",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do pre-orders work?",
            "answer": "<p>If an item has 'PREORDER' in the title - then we don't have currently at our Beserk Warehouse, and are either waiting for it to arrive or will special order it in for you. All the information about the estimated shipping date will be listed on the product page in the description.</p><p>Any other items purchased in the same order as a preorder item will be kept aside - and then everything will be sent together once the preorder item has arrived.<br/><br/><strong>For any Demonia or Pleaser preorders:</strong><br/>Once your order is placed we will special order these for you direct from the brand in the USA. These orders take around 12 business days to arrive at the Beserk Warehouse, and will then be shipped out to you via your shipping method.</p><p>So please allow at least two weeks for your order to ship (once placed), and you'll receive a shipping confirmation email with all your tracking information as soon as it has. The shipping time will then depend on the shipping option you chose at checkout.</p><p>On the rare occasion Pleaser or Demonia do not have the shoe in stock, we will contact you ASAP!<br/><br/><strong>For all other preorders:<br/></strong>These will usually have an estimated shipping date listed in the product description to let you know when to keep an eye out for your shipping confirmation email!</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_iq8kEb": {
          "type": "question",
          "name": "Do you sell gift cards?",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you sell gift cards?",
            "answer": "<p><strong>Yes we do! </strong>You can find our gift cards <a href=\"/products/beserk-gift-voucher\" title=\"Beserk | Gift Voucher\">HERE</a></p><p>Alternatively, use the Search Bar to search 'Gift Voucher'</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_WqtxLP": {
          "type": "question",
          "name": "How do I know when an item will restock?",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do I know when an item will restock?",
            "answer": "<p>We can't always give a heads up about when products will be restocking as it's always subject to change. We do try to restock products ASAP once they sell out though! This is subject to availability with our suppliers.</p><p><strong>Want to be contacted when a product restocks? </strong>Make sure you sign up for the restock notifiction! You can sign up with your email or phone number to be notified as soon as something is available again. This also helps our team know what to restock soonest</p><p><strong>Have a specific product in mind? </strong>Send a live chat through to our helpful team!</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_YRAH7a": {
          "type": "question",
          "name": "I need help with sizing",
          "settings": {
            "question": "I need help with sizing!",
            "answer": "<p>We include size charts - and sizing advice when available - on each product to help you find your perfect size! </p><h4><strong>Top 5 Tips for Finding Your Size!:</strong></h4><ol><li><strong>Use a tape measure to measure your bust/waist/hips </strong>- Comparing your measurements to the size chart will help to give you the best idea of what size will fit! <br/><br/><strong>Aren't able to measure yourself?</strong> Lay a similar item of clothing that fits you well and measure that flat across, making sure to double it!<br/><br/></li><li><strong>Check the materials - </strong>Fabrics like jersey, elastane and spandex will have some stretch to them, higher percentages will mean more stretch!</li><li><strong>Look for the fit style </strong>- Check to see if something is fitted, standard or oversized to help decide whether to size up, down or stick to your usual size! </li><li><strong>Check the brand</strong> - Brands like Punk Rave, Devil Fashion and Dark in Love tend to run small whereas brands like Hell Bunny, Foxblood and Forest Ink usually run true or large!</li><li><strong>Look at reviews</strong> - See what our wonderful customers are saying about the size and fit!</li></ol><p><strong>Still not sure?</strong> Send a live chat through to our helpful team!</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_dmYGkM": {
          "type": "question",
          "name": "Do you restock sold-out items?",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you restock sold-out items?",
            "answer": "<p>If you're worried about something selling out, we recommend ordering ASAP! Sadly we can't guarantee that we'll be able to restock every product that sells out but we do try our best! </p><p><strong>Products we won't restock:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Discontinued:</strong> If a product title ends in an asterisk (*), it has been discontinued and isn't able to be restocked.</li><li><strong>Final Sale: </strong>Final Sale items are just that - Final Sale. So like discontinued products once they're gone, they're unlikely to be restocked.<br/></li><li><strong>Limited Edition: </strong>We try our best to stock up on Limited Edition products and can sometimes restock, but not always.</li></ul><p><strong>Want to be first to know about a restock?</strong> Make sure you sign up for the restock notification on the product page!</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_FKtjet": {
          "type": "question",
          "name": "Are hair dyes safe to use / do they contain bleach?",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Are hair dyes safe to use / do they contain bleach?",
            "answer": "<p>Unless otherwise stated, none of the hair dyes we carry contain bleach as they are direct dye formulas. All hair dyes we carry are also vegan and cruelty free! </p><p><strong>Precautions:</strong> As everyone is different and skin sensitivities vary, we recommend checking the ingredients - listed in the product description - for any potential allergens and conducting a patch/strand test to make sure it's right for you!</p><p>If you're not sure, we always recommend reaching out to a hair professional familiar with fashion colours for the most tailored advice :)</p><p>If any irritation or reaction occurs, discontinue use immediately.</p><p><strong>Have more questions? </strong>Send a live chat through to the team! </p>"
          }
        },
